HOW TO COMPILE
==============

Compiling under Windows
------------------------

SUPPORTED OS

** Broken **

REQUIREMENT

- Visual Studio 10 and above
- Micosoft SDK 10 and above
- BoostPro  1.4.*
- GNU make (any version)

STEPS

- Goto trunk
- Set environment variable for Microsoft Visual studio directory
    - set DARK_HORSE_VS=<...>
    - set DARK_HORSE_BOOST=<..>
- make

Compiling under Linux (ubuntu)
-------------------------------

SUPPORTED OS

- Ubuntu x86_64

REQUIREMENTS

- GCC  4 and above
- pthread any version
- libaio
- zlib1g-dev
- zlibc
- boost-python
- python Ply
- tcmalloc-minimal0

STEPS

- Goto trunk
- make ubuntu-setup
- make

